{% comment %}
  Verdant Leaf — Testimonials Section
{% endcomment %}

<section class="section" id="testimonials">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="text-center mb-xl animate-on-scroll">
      <span class="section-label">{{ 'testimonials.label' | t }}</span>
      <h2 class="section-title">{{ 'testimonials.title' | t }}</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="testimonials__grid">
      <div class="testimonial-card animate-on-scroll stagger-1">
        <div class="testimonial-card__stars">★★★★★</div>
        <div class="testimonial-card__quote">"</div>
        <p class="testimonial-card__text">
          The Ali Shan Oolong completely changed how I think about tea. The floral notes are
          incredible — it's like drinking a mountain meadow. I've become a monthly subscriber.
        </p>
        <div class="testimonial-card__author">
          <div class="testimonial-card__avatar">S</div>
          <div>
            <div class="testimonial-card__name">Sarah Chen</div>
            <div class="testimonial-card__role">Tea Enthusiast, Portland</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="testimonial-card animate-on-scroll stagger-2">
        <div class="testimonial-card__stars">★★★★★</div>
        <div class="testimonial-card__quote">"</div>
        <p class="testimonial-card__text">
          I took the tea quiz as a complete beginner and was matched with the Sencha Reserve.
          Now I brew it every morning. The quality is noticeably superior to anything I've tried.
        </p>
        <div class="testimonial-card__author">
          <div class="testimonial-card__avatar">M</div>
          <div>
            <div class="testimonial-card__name">Marcus Williams</div>
            <div class="testimonial-card__role">Coffee Convert, Brooklyn</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="testimonial-card animate-on-scroll stagger-3">
        <div class="testimonial-card__stars">★★★★★</div>
        <div class="testimonial-card__quote">"</div>
        <p class="testimonial-card__text">
          What sets Verdant Leaf apart is the freshness. You can tell these teas were harvested
          recently — the aroma when you open the packet is simply breathtaking. Worth every penny.
        </p>
        <div class="testimonial-card__author">
          <div class="testimonial-card__avatar">A</div>
          <div>
            <div class="testimonial-card__name">Aiko Tanaka</div>
            <div class="testimonial-card__role">Tea Ceremony Practitioner, London</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "Testimonials",
  "class": "section-testimonials",
  "settings": [],
  "presets": [
    {
      "name": "Testimonials"
    }
  ]
}
{% endschema %}
